Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过过好日子就很难回头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在这里生活了十多年了 可还是不习惯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刘凤 快点回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 快点跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美的颜色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 沉浸在梦中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后成为契机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了看到刘凤先生的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}抓紧心中的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}即使被绝望和失望打垮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}最后仍会站起来 独自的Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}不能逃避的 Battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}将足迹向下一个地点延伸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}即使把白色的地图染成红色也要前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}风险和不利是导火索
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,400)}将兴奋的“确信”之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}射向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Reckless fire 如此大胆地 磨练生命之术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}这个世界是生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}无论白与黑所走的路只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}不可能熄灭 此刻心中的篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}希望能贯彻坚定不移的本能与意志
